Class HomeController

  • java.lang.Object
    • sample.HomeController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class HomeController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This Controller handles the Scene after the user has completed login. The main purpose of this stage is the user can pick if they want to go to Appointments, Reports, or Customers.
